{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji27.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给冯友兰的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给冯友兰的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1949年10月13日）友兰先生："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月五日来函已悉。我们是欢迎人们进步的。像你这样的人，过去犯过错误，现在准备改正错误，如果能实践，那是好的。也不必急于求效，可以慢慢地改，总以采取老实态度为宜。此复。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬颂教祺！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月十三日[1]冯友兰，当时是清华大学哲学系教授。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":13}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":412,"page_end":412},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}